{"tid":40730,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"NOKIA明年回歸　推200元平價機　預載「貪食蛇」遊戲","createTime":"2016-12-15T11:36:38.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-18T08:55:23.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0743520afc9ccc8ade3e383cb4fd3e19f8953aa9","tid":40730,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T11:36:38.000Z","msg":"諾基亞（NOKIA）自2014年將業務賣給微軟後就退出電話市場，如今終於有望回歸。諾基亞宣布將會推出新款機NOKIA 150，以26美元（約200港元）的超低價搶佔平價機市場。新機雖然不能上網，但電池可待機足足31天，亦會預載「貪吃蛇」這款經典遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n由諾基亞老將Arto Nummela領軍的HMD早前宣布，接手諾基亞賣給微軟的功能手機業務。HMD是與諾基亞簽訂授權協議，在未來10年可以在手機及平板業務上獨家使用諾基亞品牌。<br />\n<br />\nHMD周二宣布將會推出Nokia 150，以及同款可支持雙卡的Nokia 150 Dual SIM。新機沒有上網功能，但就可以聽收音機及MP3。NOKIA 150機身長度僅為2.4吋，並保留了實體鍵盤。<br />\n<br />\n電話的一大賣點是續航力超強，電池足以連續使用22小時，待機時間長達31天，保留了諾基亞耐用的特色，而且只售26美元。加上預載「貪吃蛇」遊戲，相信對諾基亞的「粉絲」有一定吸引力。新機設有黑白兩色，將於2017年首季在亞太、印度、中東、非洲及歐洲地區推出。<br />\n<br />\n相關報道：CNBC／WIRED<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cnbc.com/2016/12/14/nokia-phones-are-back-and-the-first-is-a-dumb-phone-with-snake-31-day-battery-life.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2016%2F12%2F14%2Fnokia-phones-are-back-and-the-first-is-a-dumb-phone-with-snake-31-day-battery-life.html&d=6dZpwG%2FIIOfku5N8VV850ksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=cfe36fc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.cnbc.com/2016/12/14/nokia-phones-are-back-and-the-first-is-a-dumb-phone-with-snake-31-day-battery-life.html</a> <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.wired.co.uk/article/nokia-150-feature-phone-snake\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.co.uk%2Farticle%2Fnokia-150-feature-phone-snake&d=6dZpwG%2FIIOfku5N8VV850ksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=820926f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.wired.co.uk/article/nokia-150-feature-phone-snake</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/technology/nokia明年回歸-推200元平價手機-預載-貪食蛇-遊戲/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Ftechnology%2Fnokia%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E5%9B%9E%E6%AD%B8-%E6%8E%A8200%E5%85%83%E5%B9%B3%E5%83%B9%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F-%E9%A0%90%E8%BC%89-%E8%B2%AA%E9%A3%9F%E8%9B%87-%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2%2F&d=6dZpwG%2FIIOfku5N8VV850ksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=aef2dc22\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Ftechnology%2Fnokia%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E5%9B%9E%E6%AD%B8-%E6%8E%A8200%E5%85%83%E5%B9%B3%E5%83%B9%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F-%E9%A0%90%E8%BC%89-%E8%B2%AA%E9%A3%9F%E8%9B%87-%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2%2F&h=3543066e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/technology/nokia明年回歸-推200元平價手機-預載-貪食蛇-遊戲/</a>"},{"pid":"a4cfc15e98047bd6fcadfad2173be4de1bea5a89","tid":40730,"uid":52068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T11:47:08.000Z","msg":"哇！黃天恩賜啊"},{"pid":"14a62d7f9f0c7b639bbb086d61a11f1e1316695a","tid":40730,"uid":44948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T11:48:25.000Z","msg":"等我摷返部3210出黎玩貪食蛇先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d86e2637ab5e0e02386972d5f654b5fef3c2c704","tid":40730,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T11:51:29.000Z","msg":"我有Nokia 215<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35f8aba1851a8e58748da4c7050d9367a193c4e5","tid":40730,"uid":23916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T12:08:28.000Z","msg":"Nokia仲未知自己衰咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ceb425553da162fc93f3d8f57f09b3a051d10a7","tid":40730,"uid":63239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T17:09:31.000Z","msg":"香港應該冇啦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e426f01e940135a85359c63fc6f188a114edc2a5","tid":40730,"uid":38390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T17:10:26.000Z","msg":"正ah"},{"pid":"3fba53029fa2cdd3166f9f72376bc166e674437d","tid":407